      "role": "user",
      "content": "i’ve been wandering through these cities for weeks now, seeing all the things i thought i needed to see. but honestly... the itinerary feels finished. it's like i've reached the last stop on the map and there's just no reason to keep booking more tickets. it feels like the journey is just... done.",
